扬声器底座，并兼作 Nest Hub Max 式智能显示器。 Android 仍然没有<em>像</em>iPadOS 那样针对大屏幕进行优化，但如果这些额外功能听起来对您有用，那么 Pixel 平板电脑值得一看。 6 月份我们给它的<a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-tablet-review-clever-accessories-transform-an-unexciting-tablet-070147119.html">评分是 85 分</a>。 （与此同时，截至撰写本文时，Galaxy Tab S9 尚未发售。）</p><h2>谷歌 Pixel 7a </h2><p><core-commerce id="876369fcdc3a4a54a9aa625712cce067" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>此次促销活动中<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0dvb2dsZS1QaXhlbC03YS1VbmxvY2tlZC1TbWFydHBob25lL2RwL0IwQlo5WE5CUkI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzE4MWQ0Ni0yZTZmLTQ0MTktOWE3Mi05YjliZjc0Mzk0ZjUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAWc-gqrBTxjcMFSk22q5EXCQdGJ2GayDRgNgchmkIsL2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoogle-Pixel-7a-Unlocked-Smartphone%2Fdp%2FB0BZ9XNBRB" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Google-Pixel-7a-Unlocked-Smartphone/dp/B0BZ9XNBRB?th=1">，Google Pixel 7a</a>降至 399 美元新低。由于其快速的 Tensor G2 芯片、流畅的 90Hz 显示屏以及对无线充电的支持，它是您目前可以获得的<a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-engadget-guide-to-the-best-midrange-smartphones-120050366.html">最好的中端手机</a>。 7a 还配备坚固的摄像头和 IP67 防水设计。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy S23 Ultra </h2><p><core-commerce id="e700bd1b81694f28ab9111723d6c4f17" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL