?th=1">55 英寸</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:46;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzZYTUNXQlI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzE4MWQ0Ni0yZTZmLTQ0MTktOWE3Mi05YjliZjc0Mzk0ZjUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAASNg10Dq5ROOmijcVo8CrI3X922vM3AihGo_Bp7oebqI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C6XMCWBR" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C6XMCWBR?th=1">65 英寸</a>型号分别降至 400 美元和 548 美元。我们以前见过这些交易，但每笔交易都创下历史新低。 U6K 在网络上获得了<a data-i13n="cpos:47;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/reviews/hisense/u6-u6k">普遍的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/content/hisense-u6k-mini-led-tv-review">积极</a><a data-i13n="cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://www.pcmag.com/reviews/hisense-65-inch-u6-series-uled-tv-65u6k">评价</a>，因为它是少数配备量子点、全阵列局部调光和迷你 LED 背光的预算级设备之一。所有这些都有助于它提供比同价位大多数电视更好的对比度和色彩量。但它对于游戏来说并不理想，因为它的刷新率仅限于 60Hz 并且缺少 HDMI 2.1 端口。一般来说，它无法与更昂贵的设备的亮度或视角相匹配，但如果您的预算比较紧张，那么它看起来是一个不错的选择。</p><p>对于一款广受好评的中端机型， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzczSDhQVlQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzE4MWQ0Ni0yZTZmLTQ0MTktOWE3Mi05YjliZjc0Mzk0ZjUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAd-LZEUuOW4OKYVsGk2VT8kkd-UBZpQhTJyVGKQVT5lC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C73H8PVT" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C73H8PVT?th=1&amp;ta