于更精确瞄准的“灵敏度离合器”，其拇指轮支持左右倾斜和更快的自由旋转模式。那个轮子有点吵，而且整个东西对于有竞争意识的玩家来说太重了，但它仍然跟踪准确并且滑动平稳。</p><h2>三星 Pro Plus microSD </h2><p><core-commerce id="ca4c0b963da04023bcda24f143f2ec09" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:58;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzFQUFdUV1Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzE4MWQ0Ni0yZTZmLTQ0MTktOWE3Mi05YjliZjc0Mzk0ZjUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAT87TOqOsJX-gJX83HMEmG3YEH9Wge4i5xos-qLFzLM_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C1PPWTWT" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C1PPWTWT">三星 Pro Plus microSD 卡</a>目前售价 20 美元。它是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:59;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-microsd-card-130038282.html">最佳 microSD 卡指南</a>中的首选，因为它是我们测试过的卡中最一致的，具有一些最佳的整体速度和好卡应具备的所有重要评级：U3、V30 和 A2。它将是您的平板电脑、智能手机或 Nintendo Switch 的绝佳选择，并且配有全尺寸适配器，以防您需要将其与相机一起使用或将其连接到计算机。</p><h2>骨干一号</h2><p><core-commerce id="7642c4a83b7a4a418d7d40cb3e2b7965" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQk1ENEtGU0w_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzE4MWQ0Ni0yZTZmLTQ0MTktOWE3Mi05YjliZjc0Mzk0ZjUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAfI8bOa6uiOSxPB39qXcqc67N0PxEGKnXYYuqJ-cBHuI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BMD4KFSL" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BMD4KFSL?th=1">Backbone One</a>是一款制作精良的游戏手柄，可卡在手机两侧，并可立即与任何支持控制器输入的游戏配合使用。通过控制台或 PC 进行云流媒体游戏也很方便。目前， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQk1ENEtGU0w_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzE4MWQ0Ni0yZTZmLTQ0MTktOWE3Mi05YjliZjc0Mzk0ZjUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAfI8bOa6uiOSxPB39qXcqc67N0PxEGKnXYYuqJ-cBHuI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BMD4KFSL" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BMD4KFSL?th=1">其 USB-C</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOFJMN1ZMS1k_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzE4MWQ0Ni0yZTZmLTQ0MTktOWE3Mi05YjliZjc0Mzk0ZjUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQeRboZJEdRQpvS9-M2wBxSLPKqKFaCUYXteHCjT-FCs&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08RL7VLKY" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08RL7VLKY?th=1">Lightning</a>型号均已降至 70 美元，即折扣 30 美元。这并不是历史最低水平，但该设备的折扣相对不常见。去年我们对 One 给予了<a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/backbone-one-ios-gamepad-review-143015385.html">积极的评价</a>，目前我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:64;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-handheld-gaming-system-140018863.html">最佳手持游戏系统</a>指南中重点强调了这一点。 Backbone 表示<a data-i13n="cpos:65;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-backbone-one-android-controller-now-supports-iphone-15-190059914.html">，USB-C 型号也可与苹果新款 iPhon