-11ee-9ff7-33852732f2e8" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/425a8830-63d4-11ee-9ff7-33852732f2e8" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Will Lipman Photography for Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Echo Dot smart speaker sits on a yellow pedestal, other abstract shapes are in the background.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Echo Dot Prime Day]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[All of Doctor Who is finally coming to BBC iPlayer]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天，BBC 宣布最终将把<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/doctor-who-chibnall-whittaker-departure-reformat-series-113012792.html"><em>《神秘博士》</em></a> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/2023/doctor-who-archive-on-bbc-iplayer">所有可用的经典剧集</a>及其所有衍生作品添加到 iPlayer 中。这是拉塞尔·T·戴维斯 (Russell T. Davies) 作为该剧主要创作力量回归后开始的工作的顶峰，也是 BBC 的一项重大变革。在一份<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.doctorwho.tv/news-and-features/over-800-episodes-of-doctor-who-programming-will-be-coming-to-bbc-iplayer">声明</a>中，该公司表示，经典剧集的每一集，以及<em>《莎拉简历险记》</em> 、 <em>《火炬木小组》</em>和《 <em>Class》</em>等衍生剧，以及制作剧集<em>《神秘博士机密》</em> ，都将于 11 月 1 日添加。</p><p> <em>《神秘博士》</em> 2005 年后的所有复兴系列均可在英国和国外的流媒体服务上广泛观看。但最初的节目很少（如果有的话）在不收取额外费用的情况下点播，因为它仍然是 BBC 最可靠的摇钱树之一。该系列已以 VHS、DVD 和现在的蓝光版本发行，其中一些最新发行的版本需要多次印刷。至少在问心无愧的情况下，点播《神秘<em>博士》的</em>唯一途径是付费购买<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-12-26-bbc-britbox-doctor-who-uk.html">BritBox 的优质流媒体服务</a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>作为发布的一部分，BBC 重点介绍了新的辅助功能（包括每集都配有手语翻译），并且新的材料档案也将在<em>《神秘博士》</em>官方网站上发布。目前还不清楚这是否包括随该剧发行的众多 DVD 和蓝光光盘附带的大量特别纪录片和幕后材料。</p><p>这一变化是在该剧同月晚些时候迎来其 60 周年纪念日之际发生的，因为该剧不再是纯粹的 BBC 制作。相反，它是由 Bad Wolf Productions 在迪士尼的现金支持下制作的，迪士尼将在英国境外的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/doctor-who-disney-plus-2023-150040129.html">Disney+</a>上播放该剧。这纯粹是我的猜测，但如果 BBC 已经解决了阻止其在英国播放《神秘博士》全部内容的任何问题，那么整个系列也可能同时在 Disney+ 上播放。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/all-of-doctor-who-is-finally-coming-to-bbc-iplayer-152006413.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/all-of-doctor-who-is-finally-coming-to-bbc-iplayer-152006413.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b76d8f8c-efd8-4df8-9aad-5c655f3a3dc6</guid><dc:creator> Daniel Cooper</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:20:06 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1696951207</ingested><modified> 2023-10-10T15:20:13+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Lifestyle]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Television]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Daniel Cooper]]></category><media:content height="1444" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/4b72db30-677f-11ee-9bff-3635ac64b416" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1444" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/4b72db30-677f-11ee-9bff-3635ac64b416" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[BBC]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Promotional image for 'Doctor Who's 60th anniversary that, awfully and terribly, decided to put Sylvester McCoy on the furthest left rather than front and center, where he should be.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Doctor Who ]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best Prime Day TV deals we could find for October 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> While Black Friday is generally the best time to grab a good TV for the lowest price possible, Amazon&#39;s <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-everything-you-need-to-know-about-october-prime-day-115842532.html">Prime Big Deal Days sale</a> — which kicked off today and runs through Wednesday — has brought a few worthwhile discounts for those looking to shop for a new set today. We&#39;ve sorted out the best TV deals of the “October Prime Day” event below, which include solid prices on LG OLED TVs, Samsung&#39;s The Frame TV and well-reviewed budget models from Hisense and TCL. If you want to spruce up your TV with a new media streamer, we&#39;ve included a handful of deals on those devices as well.</p><h2> LG C2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="2da993aa13f549e19eb312b8bffe0ae4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOVJNTExKUFg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZzPOTDuirbQ6XjUO60Hpw-Z9qAttehI4gT8ts4Dawgv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09RMLLJPX" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09RMLLJPX?th=1">55-inch LG C2</a> is down to $1,097, which is $100 more than the lowest price we&#39;ve seen for the OLED TV but still $100 less than its usual sale price these days. The C2 is a 2022 model, but <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/home-entertainment/lg-oled-c3-review-sets-the-standard-for-high-end-television-picture-quality/">various</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/features/lg-c3-vs-lg-c2">reviews</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/tools/compare/lg-c2-oled-vs-lg-c3-oled/31229/37848?usage=1&amp;threshold=0.10">suggest</a> that LG&#39;s new <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2dwL3Byb2R1Y3QvQjBCVlhGNzJIVi9yZWY9b3hfc2NfYWN0X3RpdGxlXzE_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVxNfP5LkgUDFhuFHm2bAzT3H5RehitSGkpXfo_6M7iX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BVXF72HV%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0BVXF72HV/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1">C3 TV</a> is only a marginal upgrade. The older set still provides the kind of high contrast, wide viewing angles, rich colors and smooth motion you&#39;d expect from a good OLED panel, plus it has four HDMI 2.1 ports capable of playing 4K video at 120Hz. A <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/qd-oled/">QD-OLED</a> set like the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2dwL3Byb2R1Y3QvQjBCV0ZWQ0xHOT90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xajktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImNkNTUyYjMwLTUzMDEtNDY3Yy04MzBiLWEwM2I5NzY1MDQzMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXOpkDEVpvz33UYGg9R96egmXcn66opbe1TI-5M7_Bni&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BWFVCLG9" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0BWFVCLG9">Samsung S90C</a> will deliver better brightness and color saturation, but the C2 should satisfy if you keep it out of a brightly-lit room. LG&#39;s OLED TVs also support Dolby Vision HDR, while Samsung TVs do not.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> Samsung S90C </h2><p><core-commerce id="b8480898e74044819eeba04d9593c61f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Speaking of the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2dwL3Byb2R1Y3QvQjBCV0ZWQ0xHOT90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xajktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImNkNTUyYjMwLTUzMDEtNDY3Yy04MzBiLWEwM2I5NzY1MDQzMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXOpkDEVpvz33UYGg9R96egmXcn66opbe1TI-5M7_Bni&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BWFVCLG9" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0BWFVCLG9?th=1">Samsung S90C</a> , the 55-inch version of that OLED TV is on sale for $1,448. While not cheap, this is an all-time low and about $125 off the TV&#39;s average street price. As noted above, the S90C&#39;s QD-OLED panel delivers excellent picture quality in most lighting environments, and it has just about all <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-tvs-for-gaming-180033983.html">the gaming features</a> expected from a modern set, including four HDMI 2.1 ports that can reach up to 144Hz in 4K. It won&#39;t get as bright as the best LED TVs with HDR content, but it&#39;ll provide superior contrast, motion handling and viewing angles for those willing to pay a premium.</p><h2> LG B2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="dbd596add88046aca4f1fe0a81752398" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOVJNTkQyOUI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZd6NBbDLiMpJNtsZwZbiq3v-lQsPfIjN9KXPP1BrO-5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09RMND29B" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09RMND29B?th=1">LG B2</a> , meanwhile, is down to $847 for a 55-inch model.这是一个新低，比近几个月来的平均市价低约 150 美元。 The B2 is the step-down model from the C2, as it&#39;s not as bright or color-rich with HDR content, it runs on a slower processor and it has two fewer HDMI 2.1 ports.也就是说，如果您从更基本的 LED 电视升级，它的对比度、色彩和运动性能仍然会是一个重大升级。 LG 的新款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQlZYVkxXVjcvcmVmPXR3aXN0ZXJfQjBDQjU2MVA3OD90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xajktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImNkNTUyYjMwLTUzMDEtNDY3Yy04MzBiLWEwM2I5NzY1MDQzMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAWD64u6hY3kz52yzYbmgnKvfGQxpCTLZ008TglYq5DFf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BVXVLWV7%2Fref%3Dtwister_B0CB561P78" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BVXVLWV7/ref=twister_B0CB561P78?_encoding=UTF8&amp;psc=1">B3 电视</a>承诺提供更简洁的 webOS 界面，但截至撰写本文时，其价格要高得多。如果您想要一台 1000 美元以下的 OLED 电视，B2 应该更划算。</p><h2> Hisense U8K </h2><p><core-commerce id="b89e2561cb284d309e7bebbcd6d6e050" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The 65-inch <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzczSkRNMVg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAS_Fa7CArcWKf87mQU407EbB3000NNifRCbza51uksir&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C73JDM1X" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C73JDM1X?th=1">Hisense U8K</a> is available for $998, which ties the lowest price we&#39;ve seen and comes in about $100 below its usual going rate. The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzczSDhQVlQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAS24lLMe0ivVaRf3LjHM-zvjsC2G5XUcegPpbamUGKug&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C73H8PVT" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C73H8PVT?th=1">55-inch model</a> is available for $200 less. This is one of Hisense&#39;s new TVs for 2023, and <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/reviews/hisense/u8-u8k">various</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/content/hisense-u8k-mini-led-tv-review">reviews</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.pcmag.com/reviews/hisense-65-inch-u8-series-uled-tv-65u8k">say</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/best-lcd-led-tv/">it&#39;s one</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.tomsguide.com/reviews/hisense-u8k-mini-led-google-tv">of the</a> better values in the mid-priced bracket, with impressive brightness and good contrast for an LED panel. It runs the easy-to-use Google TV interface and comes with two HDMI 2.1 ports that support 4K at 144Hz. It has other gaming-friendly features like <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.hdmi.org/spec21sub/variablerefreshrate">VRR</a> and <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.hdmi.org/spec21sub/autolowlatencymode">ALLM</a> too, plus it supports all the major HDR formats. It still won&#39;t look as rich or fluid in motion as a good OLED set, and its viewing angles are worse, but the relatively low price should help make up for that.</p><h2>海信U6K </h2><p><core-commerce id="3e87cbb6116f4a7b95d514d640393579" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text