9tL1Jva3UtU3RyZWFtaW5nLURldmljZS1WaXNpb24tUmVtb3RlL2RwL0IwOUJLQ1FZUk4_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQjw6MlNiVLgY-_UXuTLsUkXMNtwsdhHc3JL6b4LVh8C&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRoku-Streaming-Device-Vision-Remote%2Fdp%2FB09BKCQYRN" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Roku-Streaming-Device-Vision-Remote/dp/B09BKCQYRN">Streaming Stick 4K+</a> , which adds an <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:48;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1Jva3UtUmVjaGFyZ2VhYmxlLWNvbnRyb2xzLWxpc3RlbmluZy1oYW5kcy1mcmVlL2RwL0IwOTE2UkRHTUQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAT3ys5yppeSGEbcoOpy5y166XES4cIdx1hs7Q5j7jAJm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRoku-Rechargeable-controls-listening-hands-free%2Fdp%2FB0916RDGMD" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Roku-Rechargeable-controls-listening-hands-free/dp/B0916RDGMD">improved voice remote</a> with a rechargeable battery, a lost remote finder, two custom shortcut buttons, and a headphone jack for private listening without the app. That model isn&#39;t on sale as of this writing, however.</p><h2> Roku Express 4K+ </h2><p><core-commerce id="85b59fc9192a43199472094120aa99f1" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2V