olink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOEc4Skg4MzY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAASbIDzn8gA7dA6yriOIs64MloPVoIWekpZrMMJpGIpIf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08G8JH836" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08G8JH836?th=1">Roku Streambar</a> is down to $100, which is a deal we&#39;ve seen several times before but still falls about $15 below the device&#39;s average street price. This is a 14-inch soundbar that doubles as a 4K media streamer. It&#39;s a compact, 2.0-channel model, so it doesn&#39;t sound especially clear or powerful, but it&#39;s still an obvious upgrade over the speakers built into most TVs. If you&#39;re on a tight budget and want to upgrade a smaller TV outside the living room, it&#39;s worth a look. Just note that it doesn&#39;t support Dolby Vision and HDR10+, though it does work with AirPlay 2. We gave the Streambar a <a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/roku-streambar-review-133013675.html">review score of 86</a> back in 2020.</p><h2> Amazon Fire TV Cube </h2><p><core-commerce id="383ebc2567824b87ab1c359f267b0b41" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Another hybrid-style device, the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:53;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0FsbC1uZXctZmlyZS10di1jdWJlLTRrLXN0cmVhbWluZy1kZXZpY2UvZHAvQjA5QlpaM01NNz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xajktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImNkNTUyYjMwLTUzMDEtNDY3Yy04MzBiLWEwM2I5NzY1MDQzMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAToaGPqF73I6o5967VDb3FQoa1P2zxEr6ut-ys7bG1ZN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAll-new-fire-tv-cube-4k-streaming-device%2Fdp%2FB09BZZ3MM7" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/All-new-fire-tv-cube-4k-streaming-device/dp/B09BZZ3MM7">Amazon Fire TV Cube</a> blends a 4K media streamer with a hands-free Alexa speaker. It&#39;s back down to $110, which is $30 off and ties an all-time low. The Cube is Amazon&#39;s most powerful Fire TV streamer, and its HDMI pass-through lets you connect a cable box or game console and integrate it with an Alexa overlay. The device also supports Wi-Fi 6E. Fire OS&#39; frequent ads and nudging toward Amazon services may be hard to accept on a pricier device, though. The HDMI input is also limited to 60Hz video.</p><h2> Amazon Fire TV Stick </h2><p><core-commerce id="d289814e69c14cf9a9fab569f44b6b7c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:54;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOEMxVzVOODc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAS8FpxJ7HpkRlXtRXdsSroIiYnEIhm9sG4EKArJ0hVtJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08C1W5N87" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08C1W5N87">Amazon&#39;s Fire TV Stick</a> and <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:55;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOTFHNFlQNTc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARGCiOax-hVWwAbzpzikWzTd8FyArLf9uwOCjelt6PgS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB091G4YP57" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B091G4YP57">Fire TV Stick Lite</a> are on sale for $20 and $18, respectively. Neither deal is an all-time low, but both are a few bucks less than their common sale prices. You&#39;d buy one of these dongles if you wanted to add streaming content to an older 1080p TV and frequently use Amazon services like Prime Video. They aren&#39;t especially quick, and neither supports Dolby Vision, but they get the job done. Between the two, the standard Fire TV Stick&#39;s remote includes app shortcuts and TV controls for volume and power, while the Lite&#39;s remote does not. Both provide easy access to Alexa though.</p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:56;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOFhWWVoxWTU_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWo5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJjZDU1MmIzMC01MzAxLTQ2N2MtODMwYi1hMDNiOTc2NTA0MzEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdLYExrfdatbb12V4GeexuLXvPDf4EqbbpXZ9aSbeffB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08XVYZ1Y5" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08XVYZ1Y5">Fire TV Stick 4K</a> is on sale too — but only the previous-generation model, not one of the <a data-i13n="cpos:57;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/everything-amazon-announced-at-its-2023-devices-and-services-event-194621706.html">refreshed 4K or 4K Max sticks</a> Amazon unveiled in September, so we&#39;d hold off.</p><p><strong><em>您的 10 月 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:58;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:59;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-2013-201435193.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget 获取</em><a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-heres-what-to-expect-this-october-prime-day-190035290.html"><em>Prime Day 科技优惠</em></a><em>。学习关于</em><a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://www.intheknow.com/tag/prime-day/"><em>&nbsp;</em></a> In The Know 上的<a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://www.intheknow.com/post/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-2023/"><em>Prime Day 趋势</em></a><em>。听取 Autoblog 专家的意见，了解</em><em>您的汽车、车库和房屋的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1" href="https://www.autoblog.com/article/amazon-october-prime-day-2023/"><em>最佳秋季 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>，并<em>查找 AOL 专为您精心挑选的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:64;pos:1" href="https://www.aol.com/lifestyle/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-012329715.html"><em>Prime Day 促销活动</em></a>。 </p><div id="1051e9822ecb479d980fc9924b4459fe"><iframe title="Amazon Prime Big Deal Days 2023: Live Updates" src="//embed.scribblelive.com/Embed/v7.aspx?Id=3041580&amp;ThemeId=" width="500" height="600" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-amazon-prime-day-tv-deals-october-113237547.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-amazon-prime-day-tv-deals-october-113237547.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cd552b30-5301-467c-830b-a03b97650431</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:09:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1696950740</ingested><modified> 2023-10-10T15:12:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="960" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/3b63d890-66bf-11ee-b6be-717cf7622282" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="960" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/3b63d890-66bf-11ee-b6be-717cf7622282" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Amy Skorheim / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Samsung Frame TV rests flush against a white wall in a home, with a houseplant in front.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The best TV deals of Amazon's October Prime Day 2023 sale]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[X changes its policy around 'newsworthy' posts that would otherwise break rules]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/x-corp/">X</a> (formerly <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/twitter/">Twitter</a> ) has made changes to its policy on newsworthy posts to allow more content that would ordinarily violate its rules to remain on the platform. The company made the modifications amid the conflict in and around the West Bank.</p><p> Until now, the company would only grant a newsworthiness exception to accounts that had at least 100,000 followers. X has removed that threshold, as <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/10/10/x-changes-its-public-interest-policy-to-redefine-newsworthiness-of-posts/"><em>TechCrunch</em></a> reports. The latest version of the policy stipulates that “high profile” accounts are eligible for a newsworthiness exception. The account in question also needs to represent &quot;a current or potential member of a local, state, national or supra-national governmental or legislative body.&quot; Only elected officials and government figures have historically been <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-03-28-twitter-label-tweets-terms-of-service-newsworthy.html">eligible for the exemption.</a></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> X&#39;s Safety account noted there&#39;s been an upswing in daily active users in the region in recent days and that users have posted more than 50 million times about the conflict. The platform <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://x.com/safety/status/1711564133504872481"><ins>said</ins></a> that it was focused on “protecting the conversation on X” as the situation unfolds. </p><div id="390581765cf84253bc031de33c5a1843"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">In the past couple of days, we&#39;ve seen an increase in daily active users on <a href="https://twitter.com/X?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@X</a> in the conflict area, plus there have been more than 50 million posts globally focusing on the weekend&#39;s terrorist attack on Israel by Hamas.<br><br> As the events continue to unfold rapidly, a cross-company…</p> — Safety (@Safety) <a href="https://twitter.com/Safety/status/1711564133504872481?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 10, 2023</a></blockquote></div><p> “Over the weekend, we updated our <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://help.twitter.com/en/rules-and-policies/public-interest">Public Interest Policy</a> ,” the company said. “We know that it&#39;s sometimes incredibly difficult to see certain content, especially in moments like the one unfolding. In these situations, X believes that, while difficult, it&#39;s in the public&#39;s interest to understand what&#39;s happening in real time.”</p><p> X also said it had removed “newly created Hamas-affiliated accounts” and is working with partners to reduce the spread of “terrorist content.” However, the change to the newsworthiness policy could enable more misinformation about the Israel-Hamas conflict (and other issues) to remain on X when it previously would have been yanked.</p><p> The company appears to be taking a more hands-off approach to misinformation in general under owner Elon Musk. It&#39;s relying more on <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-community-notes-rolling-out-globally-195650660.html">Community Notes</a> to crowdsource contextual information about posts that may be false or misleading.</p><p> According to <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Information;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ba0a4cdc-cec8-416a-9e93-e11b8179129c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Information&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATOfm5zEqIqOs64RWW91zKe9sUumOCAYiRougy7WU-CD&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theinformation.com%2Farticles%2Felon-musks-x-cut-disinformation-fighting-tool-ahead-of-israel-hamas-conflict" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.theinformation.com/articles/elon-musks-x-cut-disinformation-fighting-tool-ahead-of-israel-hamas-conflict"><em><ins>The Information</ins></em></a> , X killed off a tool in recent months that helped to tackle coordinated misinformation campaigns by detecting when multiple accounts shared the same piece of potentially doctored or mislabelled media. The company is said to have made that move to cut costs.</p><p> X flagged several false and misleading posts regarding the conflict, including ones with a video that claimed to show Israeli airstrikes against Hamas. However, a review by <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:CNBC;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=34e37b9c-8975-48da-aa39-df8bcd5badc3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=CNBC&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5jbmJjLmNvbS8yMDIzLzEwLzA5L3gtZm9ybWVybHktdHdpdHRlci1hbXBsaWZpZXMtZGlzaW5mb3JtYXRpb24tYW1pZC10aGUtaXNyYWVsLWhhbWFzLWNvbmZsaWN0Lmh0bWwiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImZjYWJmMDExLWMyNmEtNGU4OC1iMWEyLTZlOTg5NDEwYjljYiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQwl3Z7HLxkD-WoC3lluHxbc-vrc6wyk-6-UZXa2DIKY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Fx-formerly-twitter-amplifies-disinformation-amid-the-israel-hamas-conflict.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/10/09/x-formerly-twitter-amplifies-disinformation-amid-the-israel-hamas-conflict.html"><em><ins>CNBC</ins></em></a> found that the platform&#39;s systems did not detect many other posts with the same video and caption. The tool X recently shut down may have helped in that regard.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/x-changes-its-policy-around-newsworthy-posts-that-would-otherwise-break-rules-150842429.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/x-changes-its-policy-around-newsworthy-posts-that-would-otherwise-break-rules-150842429.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> fcabf011-c26a-4e88-b1a2-6e989410b9cb</guid><dc:creator> Kris Holt</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:08:42 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1696950524</ingested><modified> 2023-10-10T15:08:49+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2504" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/1fa7c7d0-6163-11ee-bfca-b0174d604bfc" width="4457"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2504" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/1fa7c7d0-6163-11ee-bfca-b0174d604bfc" width="4457"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Trabajadores instalan un cartel de "X" en el techo de la sede de la empresa (antes Twitter) en el centro de San Francisco, 28 de julio de 2023. (AP Foto/Noah Berger, Archivo)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[UE-X DESINFORMACIÓN]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best Amazon Prime Day iPad and tablet deals for October 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Amazon&#39;s second major sales event for Prime members this year is underway, and it&#39;s brought a few noteworthy tablet deals along with it.亚马逊称之为<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-everything-you-need-to-know-about-october-prime-day-115842532.html">Prime Big Deal Days</a> ，包括各种<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">iPad</a> 、Amazon Fire slate 和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-tablet-review-clever-accessories-transform-an-unexciting-tablet-070147119.html">Google Pixel 平板电脑</a>的折扣。 For your convenience, we&#39;ve rounded up the best iPad and tablet deals we could find during this October Prime Day sale below.</p><p>请注意，并非所有折扣都是 Prime 会员独有的，而且我们总有可能在黑色星期五看到更低的价格。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://9to5mac.com/2023/10/05/ipad-mini-7-new-ipad-air-rumors/">最近的一些报道</a>称，苹果也可能在未来几个月发布新的 iPad，尤其是 iPad Air 和 iPad mini 的更新。不过，如果您现在需要一块新板，这里是我们看到的最便宜的产品。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2>苹果iPad Air </h2><p><core-commerce id="26a8ee839aa74323b2c02bed4ba982f8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOVYzSE4xS0M_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAbal_s9Xk2kj1AsIwdNHBHYqPpwC3u2dsQ5wjas9Cryd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09V3HN1KC" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09V3HN1KC?th=1">iPad Air</a>的售价为 500 美元，比直接从 Apple 购买便宜 99 美元。我们可能很快就会看到更新，但就目前而言， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">我们认为</a>现有的 iPad Air 是苹果平板电脑产品线中价格和性能的最佳结合。它为您提供与 iPad Pro 类似的优雅设计，而且价格更少，配备强大的 M1 芯片，足以满足工作和重型游戏的需要，具有令人愉悦的 10.9 英寸显示屏，USB-C 端口，并支持最新的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0FwcGxlLU1VOEYyQU0tQS1QZW5jaWwtR2VuZXJhdGlvbi9kcC9CMDdLMVdXQkpLLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby00czMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg3ZTZiM2E5LWY3NjUtNGM5Ni1hMTcwLWEyMjc4ZmRjODFlZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZfjvbrGxcjADOvNfHFfUnEsFkq1jUkvPId75nWcXAyU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation%2Fdp%2FB07K1WWBJK%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation/dp/B07K1WWBJK/">Apple Pencil</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL01hZ2ljLUtleWJvYXJkLTExLWluY2gtaVBhZC1HZW5lcmF0aW9uL2RwL0IwODYzQlFKTVM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVbR3ZbGSv4pYwEbYhO26daJFpMcTuK6vOfynGqopIcG&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMagic-Keyboard-11-inch-iPad-Generation%2Fdp%2FB0863BQJMS" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Magic-Keyboard-11-inch-iPad-Generation/dp/B0863BQJMS">妙控键盘</a>。然而，该型号只有 64GB 存储空间，并且其显示屏刷新率仅限于 60Hz。去年我们给 iPad Air 的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-air-5th-generation-review-130019050.html">评分为 90 分</a>。</p><h2>苹果 iPad（第 9 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="b1fab85448004a118cb567e20d2fd594" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOUc5Q0pNMVo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYQ8PwYGKv9J24rl9Goci22hvoGPERlwZ_IwgbWBrFzM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G9CJM1Z" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09G9CJM1Z">10.2 英寸 iPad</a>降至 249 美元，与我们见过的最优惠价格相符，比苹果标价低 80 美元。这是我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">iPad 购买指南</a>中的预算选择，当它于 2021 年底上市时，我们给它<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-9th-generation-review-143045685.html">打了 86 分</a>。它使用苹果较旧的设计语言，因此它有厚边框、Home 按钮、Lightning 端口和非-层压显示器。该型号也仅配备 64GB 不可升级存储空间。也就是说，对于休闲媒体消费、游戏和多任务处理来说，它的速度仍然足够快，而且它的显示效果仍然比大多数更便宜的平板电脑的屏幕高出一步。每次充电可持续使用 10 多个小时，而且它是最后一款带有耳机插孔的 iPad。最重要的是，它可以让您以尽可能最低的价格访问 Apple 广泛的应用程序库、强大的客户支持以及多年的操作系统更新。</p><h2>苹果 iPad（第 10 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="6891c7f01a2f4e5c80762bc60345fb2b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQkpMQ1dGTk0_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAStKbP_7r1TO0BME-N9dJUW5mMoLYugXafeTjK_boTVA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BJLCWFNM" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BJLCWFNM">第 10 代 iPad 的</a>售价为 399 美元，这是我们之前见过的价格，但仍比苹果建议零售价低 50 美元。去年我们给这款 10.9 英寸平板电脑<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-10th-generation-review-160014897.html">的评分为 85 分</a>。它介于 10.2 英寸 iPad 和 iPad Air 之间：它不像前者便宜，但缺乏后者的层压显示屏、M 系列芯片和配件支持。值得注意的是，它仅适用于第一代 Apple Pencil。尽管如此，它的外观和感觉与 Air 几乎相同，速度也不慢，而且其横向自拍相机使其更方便进行 FaceTime 通话。如果你实在无力支付 iPad Air 的费用，这是一个很好的妥协。</p><h2>苹果 iPad 迷你</h2><p><core-commerce id="b84287ec93334aa4b1e2325dd6b7b918" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple 产品线中最小的 iPad 8.3 英寸<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOUc5MUxYRlA_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQIPGyZN8kcEMpFePHDEAqmkJzFVwJ1i-rBMLdKigTCu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G91LXFP" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09G91LXFP">iPad mini</a>目前售价 400 美元。这比通常的市场价格低大约 50 美元，比苹果的标价低 99 美元。这是另一款即将进行更新的 iPad，但目前它仍然是市场上最好的紧凑型平板电脑，具有现代 iPad 的所有常见优点，而且设计更易于单手握持。早在 2021 年，我们就给它打了<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-mini-6th-generation-2021-review-130009170.html">89 分。</a>与其他非 Pro iPad 一样，最大的缺点是它的默认 64GB 不可升级存储空间。</p><h2>亚马逊 Fire HD 8 </h2><p><core-commerce id="1d485a24772c4f2ea39692308744365c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>亚马逊<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOTlaOEhMSFQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATLSnUuhLVl30lYb4J8myGWB1dnsAhFBCD4cBmGsKN8L&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB099Z8HLHT" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B099Z8HLHT">Fire HD 8</a>在 Prime Big Deal Days 活动期间降价至 60 美元，比该平板电脑的历史最低价高出 5 美元，但仍比标价低 40 美元。此折扣适用于32GB存储型号；如果您需要更多空间， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOUJHNjZXTVc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAU_7CuXXIOUZ2WYl0LErCMDBudjafA-S_s78XIB6uRZt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09BG66WMW" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09BG66WMW">64GB 版本</a>售价 75 美元。不管怎样，Fire HD 8 对于大多数人来说可能是最便宜的平板电脑：它比<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQkhaVDVTMTI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVaTYkW89XqPG_I9GinWXhMh_0V-d1HPRGaHxhx3g1E9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BHZT5S12" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BHZT5S12">Fire HD 10</a>慢，显示屏分辨率仅限于 1,280 x 800，但它很轻，一次充电可持续使用 10 个小时以上对于基本的流媒体和阅读来说，它仍然<em>足够</em>快。按照标准价格计算，这并不是最划算的，但对于 60 美元来说，很难做得更好了。</p><h2>亚马逊 Fire HD 8 Plus </h2><p><core-commerce id="4b25b806e53c4e0e9197c61e3f1650fb" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>对于大多数精打细算的购买者来说，基础款 Fire HD 8 已经足够了，但如果您愿意多花一点钱， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:20;pos:1" href="ht