0&amp;signature=AQAAAemv02Z4etcTvelow-monC_Kv3PFCfTKSq0guQ9t8Clj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fhelp%2Fcustomer%2Fdisplay.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=G3JEMFDNH3FPB4XS">伪智能显示器</a>一样使用平板电脑，这会有所帮助。</p><h2>谷歌 Pixel 平板电脑</h2><p><core-commerce id="edd573365e824913ad6901065a02c861" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> 128GB 的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzFTSEdIU1o_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAbx-CgERMJcsTGbOshuU7uYwvGJsTkLlMIyKUfMRS7K_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C1SHGHSZ" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C1SHGHSZ">​​ Google Pixel 平板电脑</a>现价 409 美元，降价 90 美元，创下新低。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzFTTDlUVzg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAfsvaCYzSEMozsh8JfDmagtvQCo9t48cUc5oBDst5znn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C1SL9TW8" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C1SL9TW8">256GB 型号</a>也以 509 美元的价格出售。虽然我们认为三星的 Galaxy Tab S9 纯粹作为平板电脑<a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-tablets-150026056.html">使用效果更好</a>，但谷歌的 11 英寸平板电脑仍然拥有清晰的 LCD 显示屏、快速的<a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-7a-review-its-got-everything-you-need-and-more-for-just-499-184517525.html">Tensor G2</a>芯片和易于握持的设计，重量仅超过一磅。然而，它的一大亮点是它可以连接到附带的充电扬声器底座，并兼作 Nest Hub Max 式智能显示器。 Android 仍然没有<em>像</em>iPadOS 那样针对大屏幕进行优化，但如果这些额外功能听起来对您有用，那么 Pixel 平板电脑值得一看。 6 月份我们给它的<a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-tablet-review-clever-accessories-transform-an-unexciting-tablet-070147119.html">评分是 85 分</a>。 （与此同时，截至撰写本文时，Galaxy Tab S9 尚未发售。）</p><h2>亚马逊 Fire Max 11 </h2><p><core-commerce id="008c0a4e677049f588467eec085a8f88" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQjFWUTFaUVk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcdajYGD27pcwEVkg9rRRpaRC8m0gwV2uuOrc2jbTvx6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B1VQ1ZQY" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0B1VQ1ZQY">Fire Max 11</a>是亚马逊最大、性能最强的平板电脑，配备 11 英寸 2,000 x 1,200 分辨率显示屏、铝制框架、令人尊敬的八核处理器和 4GB RAM。它与其他 Fire slate 具有相同的软件限制和锁屏广告，因此它的售价通常为 230 美元，但现在的售价为 150 美元，与历史最低价相当。如果你已经使用了很多亚马逊服务，并且不想花钱购买入门级 iPad，那么这可能是有道理的——只是不要指望用它来完成任何实际工作。</p><h2>亚马逊 Fire HD 10 (2021) </h2><p><core-commerce id="e388e138c15944dfbc316616a3c3609f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>最新一代<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0ZpcmUtSEQtMTAtdGFibGV0L2RwL0IwOEJYN0ZWNUw_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATKfmMKe4aQ8ACBa73tyI2u_XMxnEsdngjw0aWWnN0TB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFire-HD-10-tablet%2Fdp%2FB08BX7FV5L" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Fire-HD-10-tablet/dp/B08BX7FV5L">Fire HD 10</a>的售价为 75 美元，创下历史新低。我们不能太强烈地推荐这款产品，因为亚马逊上个月刚刚发布了其 10.1 英寸平板电脑的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ0ZZUUhGTUc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAapBxOBqRLFIkuskeyr7CNKhCV4QgvOo9xAp8IxbfUf5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CFYQHFMG" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CFYQHFMG">更新型号</a>，具有更快的性能、更轻的设计、稍微改进的相机和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0FsbC1OZXctTWFkZS1BbWF6b24tU3R5bHVzLUZpcmUvZHAvQjBCUTg5RlBTUj90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby00czMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg3ZTZiM2E5LWY3NjUtNGM5Ni1hMTcwLWEyMjc4ZmRjODFlZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdlfruWfV3s-J5SeGBkwEcSZ-GOfgx0k3yJ0TNjlwGsv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAll-New-Made-Amazon-Stylus-Fire%2Fdp%2FB0BQ89FPSR" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/All-New-Made-Amazon-Stylus-Fire/dp/B0BQ89FPSR">手写笔支持</a>。截至撰写本文时，新型号尚未打折，但如果我们在黑色星期五之前看到促销，我们不会感到惊讶。不过，如果您迫不及待地想等到那时，旧版 Fire HD 10 仍然是 Fire HD 8 的升级版，具有更宽敞的 1080p 屏幕和更快的性能。近几个月它的零售价通常在 120 美元左右。</p><h2> Amazon Fire 7 </h2><p><core-commerce id="a3fad501f16d4a5da2cacd756f38de52" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOTZXS0tLMks_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNHMzLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4N2U2YjNhOS1mNzY1LTRjOTYtYTE3MC1hMjI3OGZkYzgxZWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdWOC1COLQqEe5lICWqL4luKSeOwCYPiDlpG_GoDG-rv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB096WKKK2K" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B096WKKK2K"><ins>Amazon Fire 7</ins></a> is down to $40 for Prime Big Deal Days, which is another all-time low and $20 below its typical street price. We <a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-fire-7-review-150054618.html"><ins>strongly recommend</ins></a> paying extra for the Fire HD 8 if you can; by comparison, this 7-inch tablet has a lower-resolution (1,024 x 600) display, a slower processor and less RAM. But if you just want a second screen for dirt cheap, this is a $40 tablet that&#39;s actually functional, so it might work for (very) light use cases.</p><p><strong><em>您的 10 月 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-2013-201435193.html"